{
  "chapter": 195,
  "chapter_summary": "董家酒楼顶层梯井处，吐谷浑王子伏骞击败突厥高手慕铁雄后，与李世民、突利等各方势力形成对峙。伏骞自报自创\"伏养气功\"，言语间睥睨天下。天策府高手庞玉主动请战，提出不损物件的比武规则，伏骞欣然接受。寇仲突然插话，欲挑战李世民，却被及时赶到的红拂女截住——她正是李靖之妻，以尚未了结的战斗为由逼退寇仲。寇仲因兄弟情义不愿与嫂嫂交手，主动退让。随后伏骞与庞玉的拳脚之战一触即发，各方势力在酒楼顶层展开了一场没有硝烟的争霸较量。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "好致致，那个是否荣凤祥呢？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 15,
      "line_end": 15
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": "char_tu_li",
      "text": "突利你若要动手，何须遣手下先来送死？",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 23,
      "line_end": 24
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "胜败乃兵家常事，请问伏兄慕铁雄生死如何？其他一切可迟一步再说。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 27,
      "line_end": 29
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "阁下何人？为何要代突利发言？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "伏骞你连威震天下的秦王李世民都有眼不识泰山，却仍到中原来淌这混水，小弟也要为你抹一把冷汗。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "久闻秦王之名，今日在此得见，果是人中之龙，伏骞有礼了。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 45
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "伏兄过奖，世民愧不敢当，假若伏兄不反对，世民要派人去看视慕将军的情况。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "不必多此一举。慕兄躺一会便可自行起身。世民兄勿要怪小弟对这些下人狠施辣手，非是如此，亦难以把各位引出来。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 58
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_wang_bo",
      "speaker_name": "王薄",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "请容王某说句公道话，慕将军拦路之举，已属无礼，还公然辱及王子及族人，王子出手，亦合乎情理。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 63,
      "line_end": 65
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "胜者为王，败者为寇，所谓合乎情理，大抵如是。但王老当知中原现时形势，实没有甚么情理可言，伏王子既敢率众东来，自然知道此非是游山玩水的好时机。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 67,
      "line_end": 70
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang",
      "speaker_name": "董方",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位有话好说，能否给老朽一点薄面！",
      "tone": "恳求",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 73,
      "line_end": 74
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_rong_feng_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "荣凤祥",
      "listener": "char_dong_fang",
      "text": "董老板可知此事非只一般江湖争斗，贵楼有任何损失，一概由荣某人负责。",
      "tone": "霸气",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 77,
      "line_end": 79
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_dong_fang",
      "speaker_name": "董方",
      "listener": "char_rong_feng_xiang",
      "text": "有荣老板的一句话便够。就算把敝楼拆了，我董方也可重建另一座。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 83,
      "line_end": 85
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在下岭南宋鲁，有些许愚见，望为各位接纳。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 93,
      "line_end": 93
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": "char_song_lu",
      "text": "宋老誉满天下，乃真正侠义中人，伏某当然要听命。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 97,
      "line_end": 99
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_lu",
      "speaker_name": "宋鲁",
      "listener": "char_rong_feng_xiang",
      "text": "荣老板请勿见怪，我们这些惯走江湖的人，自爱畅意恩仇，只求痛快。但董老板曾为这楼子下过一番心血，若在这里动手始终有煮鹤焚琴，大杀风景之感，我们何不移师楼下广场，再作计较？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 105,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "庞玉",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "伏王子此言，惹得庞玉心痒难熬，忍不住要领教高明。不若我们订下规则，谁若失手损毁任何物件，便算输了如何？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 125,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": "char_pang_yu",
      "text": "若庞兄一时失手，败给在下，秦王是否亲自下场？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 135,
      "line_end": 137
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "王子果是豪气迫人，既是如此，不若小弟和王子先玩一场，免得给旁人说我李世民使的是车轮战术。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 141,
      "line_end": 143
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": "char_pang_yu",
      "text": "秦王不必有此顾虑，本人自创的'伏养气功'，专讲潜藏生息之法，一人十人都不会有多大分别，若与庞兄一战侥幸胜出，反有热身作用，占便宜的实是小弟而非世民兄。",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 159,
      "line_end": 161
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "庞玉",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "王子既有此豪语，请恕庞玉大胆冒犯，请王子赐教。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 167,
      "line_end": 169
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_shi_min",
      "speaker_name": "李世民",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "既是如此，世民自乐得在旁欣赏！",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 173,
      "line_end": 173
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tu_li",
      "speaker_name": "突利",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "如确有机缘，下一场秦王可否让给我这对王子心仪已久的仰慕者？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 177,
      "line_end": 179
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_li_shi_min",
      "text": "真有意思，既是为此，王子可否把与秦王的一场比拚让予小弟呢？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 187,
      "line_end": 189
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_fu_nv",
      "speaker_name": "红拂女",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "慕将军给何人以先天气劲封闭六脉，躺在这里呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 204
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": "char_hong_fu_nv",
      "text": "姑娘能看破在下手法，确是非凡，可否赐示芳名。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 213,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_fu_nv",
      "speaker_name": "红拂女",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "妾身的过去已死，变成无名无姓的人，王子称呼妾身作红拂女又或李夫人，均悉从尊意。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 223,
      "line_end": 225
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hong_fu_nv",
      "speaker_name": "红拂女",
      "listener": "char_kou_zhong",
      "text": "寇仲你我刚才一战尚未竟全功，你凭甚么向秦王挑战？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 227,
      "line_end": 229
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_hong_fu_nv",
      "text": "小弟服了，就收回刚才的说话，嫂子也请放小子一马吧。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 231,
      "line_end": 233
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": "char_hong_fu_nv",
      "text": "女中豪杰，令人敬佩，李夫人请上！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": "char_pang_yu",
      "text": "不知庞兄用的是甚么兵器。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "庞玉",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "兵器乃不祥之物，不宜在此地施用，何不让我们玩两手拳脚，王子意下如何？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_fu_qian",
      "speaker_name": "伏骞",
      "listener": "char_pang_yu",
      "text": "祥与不祥，只在一念之间，庞兄既有此雅兴，那伏某人另有一个提议。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_kou_zhong",
      "speaker_name": "寇仲",
      "listener": "char_song_yu_zhi",
      "text": "上战伐心，下战伐力，好致致有否为此人动心呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_pang_yu",
      "speaker_name": "庞玉",
      "listener": "char_fu_qian",
      "text": "王子请赐示。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 195,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    }
  ],
